info.name: Binge Combo
info.description: Get into the spirit of the game with the yummy trio of Tender Coconut, Strawberry Cheesecake and Alphonso Mango flavours. This delicious combo is sure to leave your taste buds stumped.

info.name: Celebration Combo
info.description: Taste the sweet joy of victory with Madagascar Chocolate, Mixed Berries and Kiwi & Pear flavours. This special combo gets you into powerplay mode with its exquisite taste

info.name: Free Hit Combo
info.description: The combo of Chocochips, Roasted Almond and Tender Coconut flavours put you on the front foot of delight. The flavours hit the sweet spot of your palate, ensuring you keep coming back for more

info.name: Joyful Combo
info.description: The tempting flavours of Sea Salt Caramel, Coffee Walnut, Madagascar Chocolate and Alphonso Mango become the stars of your team. Their delectable taste ensures the taste scoreboard is always high.

info.name: Swing Shot Combo
info.description: The superstar mix of Chocochips, Madagascar Chocolate and Roasted Almond flavours gets you cheering for more. This delightful combo is sure to be the Man of the Match every single time.

info.name: Fresh Combo
info.description: Escape to a tropical paradise with the delicious combo of fresh and chunky Sitaphal & Tender Coconut ice creams. This is your one way ticket to yumminess.

info.name: Choco Combo
info.description: Go on a marathon of heavenly and indulgent flavours like Chocochips, Belgian Chocolate and Madagascar. This one is specially crafted for those who truly love chocolate.

info.name: Delight Combo
info.description: Relish a wide spectrum of flavours such as Alphonso Mango, Tender Coconut, Sitaphal and Roasted Almond. Go for this combo when you want the perfect medley of different tastes.

info.name: Blissful Combo
info.description: Enter a state of bliss with a combo of Sitaphal and Madgascar flavours. One bite is all it takes to go into a surreal world that entices you in every way.

info.name: Wonderland Combo
info.description: Step into a wonderland of flavours like Roasted Almond, Mixed Berries, Coffee Walnut and Sitaphal. Each one brings a whole new dimension of deliciousness with every bite.
